close_reason: SDK runtime now exposes PmClient/runAction and MCP dispatches through the same SDK runner; docs/tests/temp installed-package proof/gates are complete.
body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/439\\n\\nScope: first baseline execution primitive for the SDK-first architecture. This does not complete every domain-specific primitive under pm-rjqr/pm-98cz/pm-zwpp, but it gives programmatic integrations a supported typed action executor while those domains move behind narrower SDK APIs."
